Any of the ControlNet nodes can be bypassed by using the 'Bypass' option, which is located in the right-click menu.
Avoid using anime and realistic line art ControlNets together.
Previews could cause lag with larger batches/frame count. Disable them by using 'Bypass Group Nodes'.
